{"tid":617572,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟屯門有咩可以擺落口","createTime":"2018-04-05T05:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T04:27:23.000Z","uid":40757,"like":12,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"e45c0a7df3d0650a29883a34f5c237ba56f96e73","tid":617572,"uid":40757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:21:54.000Z","msg":"住撚左屯門十幾年<br />\n好似成個屯門都冇野食咁<br />\n得一堆俾錢鳩假期，鳩monday 鳩penrice 之類吹捧既垃圾<br />\n好多時寧願自己煮，再唔係樓下食m 記大閪樂算<br />\n最撚煩係同人出街食<br />\n間間野都好撚劣食唔落手<br />\n仲要其他區食過唔錯<br />\n但開親入屯門既分店都係劣撚過出面<br />\n最後又死死地氣幫襯開到通街都係既連鎖野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呻完，此post 已完"},{"pid":"4e01e00d3ee3916433af6edbfc3260d5cb82eb7a","tid":617572,"uid":123031,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:37:15.000Z","msg":"去景峰雲川燒，開咗一排係食米線<br />\n豬頸肉墨魚咀豬扒都好出色<br />\n仲有屯市附近既橋底雞煲<br />\n龍門居個條宵夜食街都有好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93bf8709838179ffe3a7e2b75357bd8abb710071","tid":617572,"uid":116131,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:38:09.000Z","msg":"置樂喇沙？"},{"pid":"ddc3da004302d7198d9afb13eb89a156e0bdaba4","tid":617572,"uid":40757,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93bf8709838179ffe3a7e2b75357bd8abb710071","tid":617572,"uid":116131,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:38:09.000Z","msg":"置樂喇沙？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:42:19.000Z","msg":"媽媽檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd75121f0c7e6d9fa706b3eba0d0aff901591679","tid":617572,"uid":114097,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"c